const projectsData = [
  {
    id: 1,
    title: "Cattle Guard",
    description: "Cattle Guard is an AI-powered solution designed to detect Lumpy Skin Disease in cattle using deep learning. By analyzing images, it quickly identifies signs of infection, helping farmers and veterinarians take early action to prevent the spread of disease and improve livestock health.",
    link: "https://github.com/Pranamya-kulal/lumpy-skin-project",
    imageUrl: "data:image/jpeg;base64,",
    technologies: ["Python", "TensorFlow/Keras", "Custom CNN","Google Colab"],
    features: [
      "Image Upload: Users can upload cattle images for disease prediction.",
      "Custom CNN: Built a custom Convolutional Neural Network for classification.",
      "High Accuracy: Achieved 97.87% accuracy in disease detection."
    ]
  },


    {
      id: 2,
      title: "Virtual Lost and found System",
      description: "The Virtual Lost and Found System is an intuitive web-based platform designed to connect people with their misplaced belongings. It empowers users to report found items with details and pictures, and helps those who’ve lost items to search for them efficiently. ",
      link: "https://github.com/Pranamya-kulal/VirtualLostandFound",
      imageUrl: "data:image/png;base64,",
      technologies: ["MySQL", "Node.js", "Express.js","VS Code","EJS"],
      features: [
        "Item Reporting: Users can found items with pictures.",
        "Item Search: Users can search for lost items.",
        "User Authentication: Users log in with unique IDs for secure access."
      ]
    },
  
    {
      id: 3,

      title: "Smart City Complaint Management System",
      description: "The Smart City Complaint Management System is designed to efficiently handle and resolve urban issues such as broken streetlights, potholes, and water leaks. It allows residents to file complaints, which are then stored, sorted, and prioritized for resolution.",
      link: "https://github.com/Pranamya-kulal/Smart-City-Complaint-Management-System.git",
      imageUrl: "https://www.awaycabs.in/uploads/image/tour-packages/mangalore-local-tour-2/mangalore-main-2.jpeg",
      technologies: ["MySQL", "Node.js", "Express.js","VS Code","Graphs & Queues","Bootstrap"],
      features: [
        "Complaint Reporting: Residents can report urban issues with descriptions.",
        "Complaint Prioritization: Complaints are sorted and prioritized using queues..",
        "Complaint Tracking: Users can track the status and updates of their complaints."
      ] 
    },
  ];
  
  export default projectsData;
